     C* F2: O-spec col 16 = R (release device) requires a WORKSTN/ICF
     C* file. This compiler has no WORKSTN/ICF device support at all
     C* (E8), so R on a PRINTER file must be a hard compile error, not
     C* a silent no-op.
     FPFDATA  IP  F    80              DISK
     FRELOUT  O   F    132             PRINTER
     IPFDATA      AA
     I                                     1   1   0DUMMY
     ORELOUT  DR 1
     O                                 10   'YES'
